# CanvasMind Privacy Policy

**Last Updated: May 16, 2025**

If you are visually impaired or have another disability, you may access this Privacy Policy by emailing us at wenxiuh25@gmail.com.

This Privacy Policy explains how data that you share with CanvasMind is processed and protected.

The terms "user" and "you" refer to a person that uses the CanvasMind Application ("App"), visits CanvasMind website, or contacts CanvasMind.

The terms "CanvasMind" and "we" refer to the individual developer who is responsible for processing personal data as described in this Privacy Policy. CanvasMind is operated by:

Wenxiu Huang
Email: wenxiuh25@gmail.com

Please read this Privacy Policy carefully. By using the App, you consent to the data practices described in this policy.

